        "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "## SecurePath\n\n**CSPS:** 34.0/100\n\n**Architecture:** 5 security layers on AWS\n\n**Stack:** Terraform + Lambda + EventBridge + CloudTrail\n\n**Findings:** 12 total — 5 CRITICAL, 4 HIGH, 1 MEDIUM\n\n**Auto-remediation rate:** 25%\n\n[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/CorpodeanAndrei/securepath)"}
